Paarl.title: Paarl
Paarl.byline: Paarl is the third-oldest town in South Africa and is approximately 60 km to the north-west of Cape Town.

Paanajärvi National Park.title: Paanajärvi National Park
Paanajärvi National Park.byline: Paanajärvi National Park (Russian: Национальный парк Паанаярви) is in Russian Karelia, by the Finnish border.
